Package: rdftools
Type: Package
Title: Common tools for RDF data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Carl", "Boettiger", 
                  email = "cboettig@gmail.com", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1642-628X")))
Description: Utilities to format data.frames and lists into
    the Resource Description Framework (RDF) model as nquads
    using common R functions.  Also includes experimental 
    DSL for constructing SPARQL queries with dplyr-style verbs.
